{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"User interface","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/user_interface","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"\n  <ol>\n    <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions\"><strong>Extensões do navegador</strong></a></li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n      <details>\n        <summary>Começando</summary>\n        <ol>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/What_are_WebExtensions\">O que são extensões</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Your_first_WebExtension\">Sua primeira extensão</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Your_second_WebExtension\">Sua segunda extensão</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Anatomy_of_a_WebExtension\">Anotomia de uma extensão</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Examples\">Extensões de exemplo</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/What_next_\">Qual o proximo?</a></li>\n        </ol>\n      </details>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n      <details>\n        <summary>Conceitos</summary>\n        <ol>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Using_the_JavaScript_APIs\">Usando as APIs Javascript</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Content_scripts\">Scripts de conteúdo</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Match_patterns\">Padrões de correspondência</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Working_with_files\">Trabalhando com arquivos</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Internationalization\">Internacionalização</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Content_Security_Policy\">Política de Segurança de Conteúdo</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Native_messaging\">Menssagens nativas</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Differences_between_API_implementations\">Diferenças entre implementações de API</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Chrome_incompatibilities\">Incompatibilidades do Chrome</a></li>\n        </ol>\n      </details>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n      <details>\n        <summary>Interface de usuário</summary>\n        <ol>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/user_interface\">Interface de usuário</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/user_interface/Browser_action\">Botão da barra de ferramentas</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/user_interface/Page_actions\">Botão da barra de endereços</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/user_interface/Sidebars\">Barras Laterais</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/user_interface/Context_menu_items\">Itens do menu de contexto</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/user_interface/Options_pages\">Página de opções</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/user_interface/Extension_pages\">Páginas de extensão</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/user_interface/Notifications\">Notificações</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/user_interface/Omnibox\">Sugestões da barra de endereço</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/user_interface/devtools_panels\">Painéis de ferramentas do desenvolvedor</a></li>\n        </ol>\n      </details>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n      <details>\n        <summary>Como</summary>\n        <ol>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Intercept_HTTP_requests\">Interceptar solicitações HTTP</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Modify_a_web_page\">Modificar uma página da web</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Safely_inserting_external_content_into_a_page\">Insira conteúdo externo</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Sharing_objects_with_page_scripts\">Compartilhe objetos com scripts da página</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Add_a_button_to_the_toolbar\">Adicionar um botão à barra de ferramentas</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Implement_a_settings_page\">Implementar uma página de configurações</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Working_with_the_Tabs_API\">Trabalhe com a API Tabs</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Work_with_the_Bookmarks_API\">Trabalhar com a API Bookmarks</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Work_with_the_Cookies_API\">Trabalhe com a API de Cookies</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Work_with_contextual_identities\">Trabalhe com identidades contextuais</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Interact_with_the_clipboard\">Interact with the clipboard</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Build_a_cross_browser_extension\">Crie uma extensão para vários navegadores</a></li>\n        </ol>\n      </details>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n      <details>\n        <summary><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Firefox_differentiators\">Diferenciadores do Firefox</a></summary>\n      </details>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n      <details>\n        <summary>APIs JavaScript</summary>\n        <ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Browser_support_for_JavaScript_APIs\">Browser support for JavaScript APIs</a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/alarms\">alarms</a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/bookmarks\">bookmarks</a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/browserAction\">browserAction</a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/browserSettings\">browserSettings</a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/browsingData\">browsingData</a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/clipboard\">clipboard</a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/commands\">commands</a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/contentScripts\">contentScripts</a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/contextualIdentities\">contextualIdentities</a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/cookies\">cookies</a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/menus\">menus</a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/tabs\">tabs</a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/theme\">theme</a></li></ol>\n      </details>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n      <details>\n      <summary>Chaves Manifest</summary>\n        <ol>\n          <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/manifest.json\">Introdução</a></li>\n        </ol>\n      <ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/manifest.json/permissions\">permissões</a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/manifest.json/short_name\">short_name</a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/manifest.json/web_accessible_resources\">web_accessible_resources</a></li></ol>\n      </details>\n    </li>\n     <li class=\"toggle\">\n      <details>\n        <summary>Workshop de extensões</summary>\n        <ol>\n          <li><a href=\"https://extensionworkshop.com/documentation/develop/\">Desenvolver</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"https://extensionworkshop.com/documentation/publish/\">Publicar</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"https://extensionworkshop.com/documentation/manage/\">Gerenciar</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"https://extensionworkshop.com/documentation/enterprise/\">Empreendimento</a></li>\n        </ol>\n      </details>\n    </li>\n    <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/Contact_us\"><strong>Contate-Nos</strong></a></li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n      <details>\n        <summary>Canais</summary>\n        <ol>\n          <li><a href=\"https://blog.mozilla.org/addons\">Blog de complementos</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"https://discourse.mozilla.org/c/add-ons\">Fóruns complementares</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"https://chat.mozilla.org/#/room/%23addons:mozilla.org\">Add-ons chat</a></li>\n        </ol>\n      </details>\n    </li>\n  </ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>Extensions that use WebExtension APIs are provided with several user interface options so that their functionality can be made available to the user. A summary of those options is provided below, with a more detailed introduction to each user interface option in this section.</p>\n<blockquote>\n  <p><strong>Nota:</strong> For advice on using these UI components to create a great user experience in your extension, please see the <a href=\"https://extensionworkshop.com/documentation/develop/user-experience-best-practices/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">User experience best practices</a> article.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>UI option</th>\n      <th>Description</th>\n      <th>Example</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/user_interface/Browser_action\">Toolbar button</a> (browser action)</td>\n      <td>A button on the browser toolbar that dispatches an event to the extension when clicked. By default, the button is visible in all tabs.</td>\n      <td>\n        <img src=\"https://mdn.mozillademos.org/files/15751/browser-action.png\" alt=\"Example showing a toolbar button (browser action).\" loading=\"lazy\">\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Toolbar button with a <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/user_interface/Popups\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">popup (en-US)</a></td>\n      <td>A popup on a button in the browser toolbar that opens when the button is clicked. The popup is defined in an HTML document that handles the user interaction.</td>\n      <td>\n        <img src=\"https://mdn.mozillademos.org/files/15753/popup-shadow.png\" alt=\"Example of the pop-up on a toolbar button\" loading=\"lazy\">\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/user_interface/Page_actions\">Address bar button</a> (page action)</td>\n      <td>A button on the browser address bar that dispatches an event to the extension when clicked. By default, the button is hidden in all tabs.</td>\n      <td>\n        <img src=\"https://mdn.mozillademos.org/files/15745/address_bar_button.png\" alt=\"Example showing an address bar button (page action) \" loading=\"lazy\">\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Address bar button with a <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/user_interface/Popups\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">popup (en-US)</a></td>\n      <td>A popup on a button in the browser address bar that opens when the button is clicked. The popup is defined in an HTML document that handles the user interaction.</td>\n      <td>\n        <img src=\"https://mdn.mozillademos.org/files/15747/page_action_popup.png\" alt=\"Example of a popup on the address bar button\" loading=\"lazy\">\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/user_interface/Context_menu_items\">Context menu item</a></td>\n      <td>Menu items, checkboxes, and radio buttons on one or more of the browser's context menus. Also, menus can be structured by adding separators. When menu items are clicked, an event is dispatched to the extension.</td>\n      <td>\n        <img src=\"https://mdn.mozillademos.org/files/15756/context_menu_example.png\" alt=\"Example of content menu items added by a WebExtension, from the context-menu-demo example\" loading=\"lazy\">\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/user_interface/Sidebars\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Sidebar (en-US)</a></td>\n      <td>An HTML document displayed next to a web page, with the option for unique content per page. The sidebar is opened when the extension is installed, then obeys the user's sidebar visibility selection. User interaction within the sidebar is handled by its HTML document.</td>\n      <td>\n        <img src=\"https://mdn.mozillademos.org/files/15755/bookmarks-sidebar.png\" alt=\"Example of a sidebar\" loading=\"lazy\">\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/user_interface/Options_pages\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Options page (en-US)</a></td>\n      <td>A page that enables you to define preferences for your extension that your users can change. The user can access this page from the browser's add-ons manager.</td>\n      <td>\n        <img src=\"https://mdn.mozillademos.org/files/15748/options_page.png\" alt=\"Example showing the options page content added in the favorite colors example.\" loading=\"lazy\">\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/user_interface/Extension_pages\">Extension page</a></td>\n      <td>Use web pages included in your extension to provide forms, help, or any other content required, within windows or tabs.</td>\n      <td>\n        <img src=\"https://mdn.mozillademos.org/files/15752/bundled_page_as_panel_small.png\" alt=\"Example of a simple bundled page displayed as a detached panel.\" loading=\"lazy\">\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/user_interface/Notifications\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Notification (en-US)</a></td>\n      <td>Transient notifications displayed to the user through the underlying operating system's notifications mechanism. Dispatches an event to the extension when the user clicks a notification, or when a notification closes (either automatically or at the user's request).</td>\n      <td>\n        <img src=\"https://mdn.mozillademos.org/files/15754/notify-shadowed.png\" alt=\"Example of an extension triggered system notification\" loading=\"lazy\">\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/user_interface/Omnibox\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Address bar suggestion (en-US)</a></td>\n      <td>Offer custom address bar suggestions when the user enters a keyword.</td>\n      <td>\n        <img src=\"https://mdn.mozillademos.org/files/15749/omnibox_example_small.png\" alt=\"Example showing the result of the firefox_code_search WebExtension's customization of the address bar suggestions.\" loading=\"lazy\">\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/user_interface/devtools_panels\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Developer tools panel (en-US)</a></td>\n      <td>A tab with an associated HTML document that displays in the browser's developer tools.</td>\n      <td>\n        <img src=\"https://mdn.mozillademos.org/files/15746/developer_panel_tab.png\" alt=\"Example showing the result of the firefox_code_search WebExtension's customization of the address bar suggestions.\" loading=\"lazy\">\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n<p>The following how-to guides provide step-by-step guidance to creating some of these user interface options:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://extensionworkshop.com/documentation/develop/build-an-accessible-extension/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Accessibility guidelines</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Add_a_button_to_the_toolbar\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Add a button to the toolbar (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/user_interface/Browser_styles\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Browser styles (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Extending_the_developer_tools\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Extending the developer tools (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Implement_a_settings_page\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Implement a settings page (en-US)</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"Extensions that use WebExtension APIs are provided with several user interface options so that their functionality can be made available to the user. A summary of those options is provided below, with a more detailed introduction to each user interface option in this section.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"User interface","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"User interface","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Interface utilisateur","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"ユーザーインターフェイス","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"User interface","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Пользовательский интерфейс","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"User interface","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"用戶介面","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/mozilla/add-ons/webextensions/user_interface","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/mozilla/add-ons/webextensions/user_interface/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla","title":"Mozilla"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons","title":"Complementos"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions","title":"Extensões do navegador"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/user_interface","title":"User interface"}],"pageTitle":"User interface - Mozilla | MDN","noIndexing":false}}